Package wt.events

Defines KeyedEvents which are dispatched by a KeyedEventDispatcher and�listened for by a KeyedEventListener; KeyedEvents can be grouped by a KeyedEventBranch.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    KeyedEventBranch
    An KeyedEventBranch represents a group of events to which listeners may subscribe.
    KeyedEventDispatcher
    Interface for event subscription and notification.
